commitResults.messageTitle: Refactor all Files: Rename Person to Student
commitResults.messageBody:
Currently, some Files kept the term "Person" or had variables with the term "Person".
Since our team wishes to avoid confusing between "person" & "student", we have decided to adopt the terminology as "person".
Therefore, all File Names & Varaibles containing "person" have been renamed to "student".

Let's continue to adopt ther term "student" for TAHub.

As such, every command now has a Command Type.

Let's include a Command Type for every new Command we create moving forward.
